overview: After eleven years Death Angel, one of the creators of thrash metal, returned to Wacken and unleashed their strength again!  Songs: 00:00​ Seemingly Endless Time, 04:11​ Son of the Morning, 09:46​ Claws in so Deep, 15:24​ Buried Alive, 23:41​ Voracious Souls, 30:10​ Succubus, 36:53​ The Dream Calls for Blood, 42:13​ The Ultraviolence-Intro, 43:35​ Mistress of Pain.
title: Death Angel: Live at Wacken
